OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Parker
OL,5,FRon Parker, Age 100, Royal Engineers
OL,7,FInterviewed 3 April 2024
OL,9,FCalled up at aged 18 to train with the
OL,10,FRoyal Sussex Regiment, Mr Parker from
OL,11,FWorthing then joined the Royal
OL,12,FEngineers and was sent to France a
OL,13,Ffortnight after the landings.
OL,15,F"After D-Day we gradually made our way
OL,16,Fdown to Portsmouth and the Isle of
OL,17,FWight," he said.
OL,19,F"We were on standby all the time,
OL,20,Ffully equipped so we could go at a
OL,21,Fmoment's notice which we did.
