OL,5,F"We would go out and find out the
OL,6,Freason why a landing craft was stuck.
OL,7,FSometimes it was because the petrol
OL,8,Fhadn't been turned on.
OL,10,F"Space was limited and there were so
OL,11,Fmany men coming in."
OL,13,FThis work ensured there were fewer
OL,14,Fblockages on the beaches at a time
OL,15,Fwhen more and more ships were landing
OL,16,Fwith vehicles and supplies.
